      &lt;img alt="Acer Predator GD711 projector" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TuT8O579hQbg6kQCT-Sm1M9ANyc=/1x0:1972x1314/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69988526/gd711hero.0.jpg" /&gt;
